          "target": "仅限桌面应用。Typst 支持 ttf/otf/ttc/otc 格式。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "The string next to the font name is used to identify fonts that share the same PostScript name.",
          "target": "字体名称旁边的字符串用于标识共享相同 PostScript 名称的字体。"
